	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=22775"><span id="Sage">SuBoneTL</span></a><br /><b><span id="Sage">Sage</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">137 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Matchless Dragonhide Armor drops randomly from all the various dragons that inhabit the Western Wastes.&nbsp;&nbsp;These dragons all drop worked, reinforced, heavy, peerless, and matchless armor.  Matchless is the best of those.  Depending on the level of the dragon, it will drop more often than the others.  A full suit of matchless armor gives the following stat bonuses.<br/><br/>155 hp/mana<br/>220 AC<br/>34 STR<br/>24 STA<br/>23 AGI<br/>20 DEX<br/>42 WIS<br/>19  INT<br/>35 CHA<br/>14 mag<br/>27 fir<br/>7 cld<br/>16 pois<br/>15 dis<br/><br/>The set is great for a wisdom based hybrid, moreso for the ranger because it gives more AC than Tolan's, only a bit more than Runed Scout's, but much better stats.  Basically this armor rocks for any melee class.  And with a Talisman from any of the more powerful dragons, there's 6-7 more to each stat, and 30-40 hp/mana, depending on which dragon.  Well...  Hope this helps.<br/><br/><br/></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br /><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=84779 target=akztarg>Mystikefini Ali</a><br/>Forest Stalker of Brell Serilis<br/>Hero of the Dain</td></tr>
